Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.90,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:38.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The sixth round of the first stage of \Nthe Royal Knights Selection Exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:41.99,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Creation Magic: Full Metal Fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:45.06,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Magic: Thunderbolt Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:48.61,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:51.19,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Flapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:52.32,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:55.24,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:57.41,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:00:59.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:03.87,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Luck shows an extraordinary \Namount of growth and teamwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.75,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,giving K Team their victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:08.33,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In the eighth and final round \Nof the first stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Time for Yuno and Noelle's team!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:13.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:15.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A House of Silva battle \Nbetween Noelle and Solid...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:20.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And a battle between Yuno, \Nwho is favored by Vangeance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:26.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and Alecdora, who resents him over that fact.\NTwo battles filled with bad blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:30.82,main,Alec,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who will make \NMaster Vangeance's dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:34.33,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Magic: Towering Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:38.32,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about \Nother people's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:42.03,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The only dreams I see are my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.42,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The crystal has been destroyed! P Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:53.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not weak anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:27.02,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Peasant Trap
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:29.94,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.65,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Im...possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:39.01,main,Alec,0000,0000,0000,,My ultimate spell was so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:44.11,main,Alec,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even use his spirit magic.\NHe wasn't even serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:48.37,main,Alec,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the one to make Master \NVangeance's dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Once you elites trip up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.85,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,you're so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Great job winning, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.28,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You too, weed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a weed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.02,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:06.04,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.06,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your usual after-battle dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.98,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Replenishing my energy is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.40,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'll be sure to savor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.90,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'll be sure to savor it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.03,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:29.61,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Miz Charmy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.79,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:38.22,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! Who do you \Nthink you are, you fivehead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:41.54,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,I'll suffocate you by stuffing \Nmy scales into your nostrils!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.55,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, and that, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:49.86,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,That was fantastic, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:52.57,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were that amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:56.39,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally different when \Nyou're using your mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.96,flashbackitalics,En,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Solid's remarks before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:06.20,flashbackitalics,En,0000,0000,0000,,A big brother should never say \Nsuch things to his little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:13.20,flashback,Mushroom,0000,0000,0000,,Big brothers exist to protect the younger, \Nweaker siblings born after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:17.06,flashback,Mush,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you've only said \Nhurtful things to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:20.46,flashback,Mush,0000,0000,0000,,Get him, Noelle! Thrash your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:25.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know... Thanks for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.85,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,You did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:35.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think you're doing?!\N I'm royalty, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.19,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best in the next match, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:43.29,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to my Mana Skin training, \NI have much better control over my mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:48.07,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep this up and be \Nselected as one of the Royal Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:52.20,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so many excellent matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:54.37,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait until the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.87,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Entertain me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.88,italics,King,0000,0000,0000,,To think both of the peasants who humiliated \Nme made it through the first stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.17,italics,King,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and lose already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.59,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we jump right into stage two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.39,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:12.10,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.31,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The stage is changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.65,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier to judge your abilities when
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:37.34,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,you're forced to fight in\Na variety of situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.39,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.63,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:47.34,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... For stage two,\N you'll be fighting upon this stage.
