Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:55.33,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The stage may have changed, \Nbut my beauty remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.66,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.75,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for the fate of you filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.69,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure there's no trace of \Nyou left. I hope you're prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:05.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm not that easy to get rid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:08.11,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta isn't filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.65,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should \Nbe prepared, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:14.54,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! No holding back, you got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:17.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't dream of it, Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:19.49,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,At least you're spirited, Funglasquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.42,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me Funglasquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.92,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Welp, looks like we're \Nfacing off with royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:29.18,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best with teamwork again, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:35.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You looked anxious when they \Nshifted the stage around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You probably have other \Ntraps set up, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:44.35,italics,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,This brat... That's right. He can read other people's ki or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.94,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.84,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,I set up a bunch of traps \Naround the stage yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:57.33,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,I heard intel that the \Nexam would be held here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:04.50,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Intel? But the location of the Royal Knights \NSelection Exam must've been top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.79,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You set them up yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} cheating, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:13.54,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think that, you dumb shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.06,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering intel counts as an ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.14,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a rule against setting \Ntraps up the day before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.14,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Well? They haven't called \Nme out on it, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.63,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,And he already got argued into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.51,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This side of Asta is adorable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:34.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell us where the traps are,\Nsince we're on your team!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We can at least help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.91,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.92,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell you, our enemies \Nwill probably figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:43.21,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:46.46,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle this my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:52.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Then I'll handle things \Nmy own way, too, ya jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.17,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be arguing about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.97,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:59.12,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They do say that the more you fight,\Nthe closer you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.99,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You should fight with me, too, \Nsomeday. In a friendly way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:07.40,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully you can think up something \Nwith that shitty little brain of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My brain's so big that my \Nskull can barely contain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.77,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! The only thing small \Nabout Asta is his height.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:19.45,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:25.79,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,B Team: Xerx, Mimosa, and Asta \Nversus C Team: Kirsch, Sol, and Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:29.21,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Round one of stage two... Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.00,sign_10224_102_Sol___Kirsch___M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Xerx   Mimosa   Asta
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.00,sign_10224_103_C_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}B Team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.00,sign_10224_104_Cesc___Adrian___,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Magna   Sol   Kirsch
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.00,sign_10224_105_D_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}C Team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:42.14,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa... It seems she's \Nlost sight of herself after
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.62,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,being exposed to such \Nboorish mana for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:45.85,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The poor dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:51.70,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll free you from those filthy wretches \Nbefore you even have a chance to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.99,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry Blossom Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:05.42,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Cherry Blossom Storm of Petals \N~Plus My Beautiful Illusion~.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.71,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:14.05,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty! Time for \Na flower-viewing party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.18,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:23.67,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Now, repent your filthy selves \Nwithin my beautiful spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.56,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:34.69,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I talked big, but I can't think of \Na way to break through this spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.08,italics,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to sit tight for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.32,italics,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,We're better off waiting for them \Nto set off the magic traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:44.83,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What an awesome spell. I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.83,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.21,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:00.22,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right... Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:04.47,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looks like something \Namazing's about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:12.48,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Good... That's it. Go even deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.94,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:20.93,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,More... More intense...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:29.41,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this? It's not magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.12,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It's so powerful, intense,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.46,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.30,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:47.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Black Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:54.02,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,The cherry blossoms... Wait, forget that!\NThe traps I'd set up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.56,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.26,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This is from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.76,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}So this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.39,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I knew he had been training ever \Nsince he went to the volcano,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.76,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}but to think his power was this immense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.87,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Way to go, Asta, my BFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The cherry blossoms are being erased!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:24.97,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... What is \Nthat horrific black mass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:40.65,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,That little shrimp... blew away \Nall the magic in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:46.23,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's amazing, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.49,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you do, you little shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:53.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just heard the \Nreal you for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:58.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.30,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,You little shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:07.05,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.32,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.85,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:15.22,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's going to continue to get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.15,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,And so will I!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:22.53,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Asta's learned \Nanother interesting power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.94,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.78,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:30.14,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,You just erased all the traps I'd set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:34.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess that's a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:38.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Think up a strategy for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One that'll let all three of us win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.43,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:47.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're tricky and clever, so I'm \Nsure you can think of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:51.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, think up some sneaky \Nstrategies fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.02,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,The hell? That's a contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.10,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. Asta is \Nacting the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:03.62,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Just use that power of yours \Nand defeat them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.03,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:12.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you! Once I use that power, \NI can't use it again for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.55,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you sound so happy, you little shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.50,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Are you messed up in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:21.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fight as a team, ya jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:24.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you set up traps yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just let Mimosa and me in on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're fighting to be selected \Nas the Royal Knights who'll
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:34.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,fight against the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:38.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No one can fight them alone! \NNot me or anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:43.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work with all the powerful guys \Nhere and beat some other powerful people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.36,flashbackitalics,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Zora,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:50.07,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:54.08,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how amazing they are, \Neven a Magic Knight can't fight alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.86,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,They trust their companions and \Novercome deadly situations together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:05.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, one of the powerful \Nguys we're up against now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,is royalty and the vice captain \Nof the Coral Peacocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hit 'em with all we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:18.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What the heck was that for, ya jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:22.10,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of \Ngetting chummy with a royal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:26.23,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,But for the sake of my goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:30.74,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of any way around it, \Nso I'll use you, you little shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:36.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine with me, as long as we fight \Ntogether, you cool-masked jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:44.89,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, my magic attribute is ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:47.09,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,My specialty is trap spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:49.88,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean I can instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.76,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,set up big traps like the one \NI used in the last match.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:57.06,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Setting big traps takes time and mana,\Nand how much you put into them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.21,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,determines their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:01.27,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I pulled an all-nighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.60,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,You were serious about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:07.33,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,And you went and thrashed them \Nall like they were nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:09.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What was I supposed to do, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:17.50,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... There are three basic \Ntypes I could set up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:18.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:22.16,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Number one: binding traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.15,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever touches the magic \Ncircle gets tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.00,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Number two: pitfall traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:33.79,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Just like it sounds. Dig a hole \Nand drop someone into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:37.62,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Number three: landmine traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:40.58,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Make a simple attack spell \Nactivate on a certain spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.32,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,They'll all disappear after one use,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.62,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,and unless I take the time to \Npour lots of mana into them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.61,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,they won't be all that powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.86,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,So... What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:55.82,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,U-Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:17:01.74,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,My beautiful spell was defiled by \Nthat peasant's pitch-black thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.58,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:08.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He'd been practicing his \Ntechniques like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:11.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he'd figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.27,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling everyone not to \Nunderestimate peasants, aren't you, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.21,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a peasant myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:20.01,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're also a peasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.60,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with that, Mr. Royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.06,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Eek! I'm going to be defiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.52,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fight alongside a peasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the... Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:37.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You damn narcissist! \NThe hell is your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:41.45,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle this on my own! \NI'll finish them off myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.53,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You two, protect the crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.50,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.42,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll just do whatever \Nthe hell I want, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:55.34,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Could men be any dumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:18:02.39,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Peasants are those with meager magic. \NThat also means they're unclean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:09.16,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,They must not share the same stage as \Nus royals, the fairest of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:15.67,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa is heading toward our crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:19.91,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense that Xerx \Nfellow's magic over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:24.15,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,As for that filth, I sense \Nabsolutely no magic from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.95,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of foul creature is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.02,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:32.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, here comes Mimosa's big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:34.29,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, you filthy boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:39.41,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry Blossom Magic: Dance of the \NBeautiful Cherry Blossom Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:52.61,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Some got through those tiny little gaps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:56.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you really are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:58.90,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the unsightly way he's fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.11,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:06.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.85,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,It's faint, but I sense magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:12.75,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to lure me into a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.19,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I can see right through your unsightly ploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:20.43,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry Blossom Magic: My Beautiful Clones!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:34.40,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Did you actually think I'd \Nfall for such crude traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:38.09,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,And you went into a narrow place where \Nyou'll have trouble swinging your sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:41.32,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,with no place to run. You couldn't be uglier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:45.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I thought this \Nwas a great plan, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.04,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Wither and fall, you peasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.18,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:10.22,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I erased all of the trap spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.07,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:19.70,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,You keep counting on your magic detection\N'cause it has higher specs than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:22.63,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you fell for our low-spec,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:26.13,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,plain and simple trap that \Nwe got all sweaty digging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.26,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Some high and mighty royal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:33.18,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,They physically dug this up \Nwithout using any magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:39.21,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly! I'll just fly \Nright out of this primitive—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad about doing \Nthis to Mimosa's big bro,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I need you to pass out for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.97,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.64,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now we finally feel like a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.58,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,I just used you, dummy.
