Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:49.34,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:54.01,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}The Life of a Narcissist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:53.31,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The Life of a Narcissist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:57.14,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Please do stop crying, Master Kirsch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:23:01.15,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since he was born, he was \Nonly interested in his own beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:06.10,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no. No one is more beautiful than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:08.92,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't be satisfied with the \Nbeauty of any of his wooers,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:10.41,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,so he spent his whole life single.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:15.27,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Because of his warped personality, \Nhe was abandoned by those around him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:17.62,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,and spent his later years alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:23.13,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm thirsty... Oh? I'm so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:27.08,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still oh so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:31.23,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,And so, his life came to a tragic end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:33.14,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:36.98,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish I could make \Nyou come to a tragic end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.44,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about teammates?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:45.52,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only using everyone \Nto achieve my own goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:51.10,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 79: \N"Mister Delinquent vs. Muscle Runt."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 79\N\N{\fs18} Mister Delinquent vs. Muscle Runt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:53.99,main,Xerx,0000,0000,0000,,Sneakily setting up traps is my magic.
